.Dd June 7, 2024
.Dt DUMPGAME 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm dumpgame
.Nd extract rom set information from ckmame database
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Brq Fl b | Fl Fl brief
.Op Brq Fl D Ar dbfile | Fl Fl rom-db Ar dbfile
.Op Ar game
.Nm
.Fl c | Fl Fl checksum
.Op Brq Fl D Ar dbfile | Fl -db Ar dbfile
.Ar checksum
.Op Ar ...
.Nm
.Op Fl hV
.Op Fl Fl all-sets
.Op Fl Fl dats
.Op Fl Fl detector
.Op Fl Fl disks
.Op Fl Fl games
.Op Fl Fl hash-types
.Op Fl Fl help
.Op Fl Fl list-sets
.Op Fl Fl mia
.Op Fl Fl set Ar pattern
.Op Fl Fl summary
.Op Fl Fl version
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
extracts rom set information from a
.Xr ckmame 1
database.
.Nm
can also find roms matching a particular checksum.
.Pp
.Nm
supports the following options:
.Bl -tag -width 27n
.It Fl Fl all-sets
Do the action for all configured sets.
.It Fl b , Fl Fl brief
Use brief mode: don't output ROM and disk information.
.It Fl c , Fl Fl checksum
Look for a ROM or disk by checksum (instead of the default
behaviour to look for a game by name).
.It Fl D Ar dbfile , Fl Fl rom-db Ar dbfile
Use database
.Ar dbfile
instead of the default
.Dq Pa mame.db .
.It Fl Fl dats
Names of the datfiles used for creating the database, and their
descriptions.
.It Fl Fl detector
Name and version of the CMPro XML header skip detector used (if any).
.It Fl Fl disks
List names of all disks in the database.
.It Fl Fl games
List names of all games in the database.
.It Fl Fl hash-types
Types of checksums used (crc, md5, sha1).
One line each for roms and disks.
.It Fl h , Fl Fl help
Display a short help message.
.It Fl Fl list-sets
List all configured sets.
.It Fl Fl mia
List names of games containing ROMs that are marked as mia in the database.
.It Fl Fl set Ar pattern
Run
.Nm
for all sets matching
.Ar pattern .
.It Fl Fl summary
List some statistics about the contents of the database.
.It Fl V , Fl Fl version
Display program name and version number.
.El
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Bl -tag -width 10n
.It Ev MAMEDB
Location for the database file.
Can be overridden with the
.Fl D
option.
Defaults to
.Dq Pa mame.db .
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
Display rom information for the game
.Dq pacman :
.Dl Ic dumpgame pacman
Display all roms matching the checksum
.Dq c1e6ab10 :
.Dl Ic dumpgame -c c1e6ab10
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr mkmamedb 1 ,
.Xr ckmamerc 5
.Sh AUTHORS
.An -nosplit
.Nm
was written by
.An Dieter Baron Aq Mt dillo@nih.at
and
.An Thomas Klausner Aq Mt wiz@gatalith.at .
